725653f-a.title: Queens: 78th Street - 57th Avenue
725653f-a.text:
78th Street, north of Fifty-eighth Ave. to Fifty-seventh Ave.
The Caldwell Riding Academy occupies the barn on the extreme left.
A group of the Brooklyn Union Gas Company tanks occupy the back-
ground.
August 1934.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
